snippet.title: Magicka 2 - Karaoke Singalong Trailer [EU]
snippet.description:
To make your own karaoke video: http://pdxint.at/magicka2singalong
Song now on Spotify: http://open.spotify.com/track/4LjcdvVC2Sq7l1NmyQk84V

In celebration of Magicka 2, we’ve opened a contest for anyone who wants to sing their own version of the karaoke video we just showed you! Ambitious and foolhardy songsmiths can grab an instrumental version of the song from the trailer, along with an .mp4 video file with the lyrics. Sing along, create your own karaoke video, and you can win a sweet prize! 

Music Production by: Red Pipe
Visual Effects by: Bläck

Full details are over at http://pdxint.at/magicka2singalong
